===Noun===
'''lark'''

# Any of various small [[passerine]] [[bird]]s of the family ''[[Alaudidae]]''.
# A bit of fun.
# One who [[wake]]s early; one who is [[up with the larks]].
# Slang term for someone who is mentally challenged, "Richard acts like a lark."

